room_title: Escape room "The Toy Room" by Creative Escape in Muldrow
room_description: A toy room once filled with laughter and fun is now only filled with secrets and silence. The children are missing with only a ransom note in sight! "Return what is ours if you want to see them again" is all that is written! Can you solve the puzzles and crack the codes to find and return what was wrongfully taken?
